(44, 1, '2023-09-09 15:08:00', '2023-09-09 15:08:00', '<p class=\"irIKAp\">Cho mng n vi ca hng Aokang</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Chng ti ch mun mang n cho bn nhng sn phm tt nht, thnh hnh nht, cht lng tt nht v gi r nht.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Thi trang l mt phn ca khng kh hng ngy v n thay i mi lc vi tt c cc s kin.!</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Hy bt u mua sm vui v!</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Ca hng Aokang tp trung vo hng pht trin v xu hng ca qun o thi trang, c kh nng thit k v phong cch thit k ring, sc mnh ca nh my mnh m v c khch hng yu thch su sc ~~</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Ca hng Aokang mang n cho bn mu sc ca th gii, dch v trc v sau bn hng hon ho,  mi ngi bit chng ti ang di chuyn v thu hoch ~~</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">#Thi trang aokangdian thc s rt n gin</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Mo mua hng:</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">1. Nu bn mun chn mt kch thc, vui lng tham kho biu  kch thc. Nu bn khng chc mnh ang mc size no, bn c th cung cp chiu cao v cn nng ca mnh v chng ti s t vn chuyn nghip cho bn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">2. Tt c cc sn phm s c vn chuyn t Trung Quc trong vng 48 gi sau khi t hng. Sau , n s c giao cho bn trong vng 5 n 10 ngy . Sau khi chng ti gi hng, h thng hu cn s khng hin th hng  c vn chuyn ngay lp tc, v nhng hng ha ny s c gi n kho trung chuyn quc t trc. Sau khi nhn vin kho cung cp nhng mt hng ny, h thng cp nht thng tin hu cn. Hy kin nhn ~~ Cm n bn</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">3. Nu khng th m c cc l cc ca qun jean hoc qun o denim, xin ng lo lng. Chng khng phi l nhng sn phm b li cha hon thnh. Tt c qun jean hon ton mi t Trung Quc i lc m bo tnh ton vn ca sn phm  mc  cao nht, v s khng c s m ca ngu nhin!</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">4. Chng ti s kim tra cn thn trc khi giao hng, nhng i khi n s b b st. V d: bn khm ph ra cc li, thiu st v cc vn  v cht lng sau khi nhn c hng. Vui lng lin h vi chng ti cng sm cng tt. Chng ti chn thnh v c trch nhim ~~</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">5. Nu bn hi lng vi sn phm v dch v ca chng ti, xin vui lng cho chng ti 5 sao Cm n cc bn  ng h v chc cc bn sng vui v ~~~</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Mi im u quan trng i vi ca hng ca chng ti. Cm n tt c cc khch hng  thch</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Chng ti s lun c sn phm mi. Hy tip tc ch  n cc tin tc mi nht ca chng ti. Chng ti s gi cho bn phiu gim gi v chit khu sn phm.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">6. Rt QUAN TRNG: Vui lng kim tra xem s in thoi v a ch ca bn c chnh xc khng. Nu c li trc khi bm t hng chng ti khng th thay i hoc sa i bt c th g </p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Li khuyn ch :</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Bi v cc phng php o lng khc nhau, cho php sai s 2-5cm, v phm vi li khng phi l vn  cht lng!</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Lu : Chng ti gi t Trung Quc i lc. Kch thc khc vi Philippines. Bn c th kim tra kch thc khi t hng  trnh nhng tn tht khng ng c. Cm n!!</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Chng ti bit rng sn phm ca chng ti khng th lm hi lng tt c mi ngi. Nu bn tm thy mt vn , bn c th lin h vi chng ti, ti tin rng chng ti c th gii quyt vn  cho bn. Chng ti  y  phc v bn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Chc mt ngy tt lnh!</p>', 'o S Mi Nam Di Tay C B Form Rng Thi Trang Hn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ao-so-mi-nam-dai-tay-co-be-form-rong-thoi-trang-han', '', '', '2023-09-09 15:08:01', '2023-09-09 15:08:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/web1/?post_type=product&#038;p=44', 0, 'product', '', 0),
